rows.label: tlk70000137_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I suggested that His Majesty might
return to Superbia and rest...

rows.label: tlk70000137_02_msg0002
rows.name: But he just shook his head at me.

rows.label: tlk70000137_02_msg0003
rows.name:
His Majesty said stopping
the Holy Grail was more
important than anything else.

rows.label: tlk70000137_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Not just for Superbia
but for all of Alst.

rows.label: tlk70000137_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm bound to follow His Majesty in
all things, so I can only agree.
